(III. POLICY STATEMENT) Tj
-50 -383 Td
/F1 9 Tf
50 370 Td
(  1. All system access requires unique user credentials; sharing is prohibited.) Tj
-50 -370 Td
50 358 Td
(  2. Password complexity: minimum 8 characters with uppercase, number, and symbol.) Tj
-50 -358 Td
50 346 Td
(  3. Multi-factor authentication required for administrative and sensitive access.) Tj
-50 -346 Td
50 334 Td
(  4. All data in transit must be encrypted using TLS 1.2 or higher.) Tj
-50 -334 Td
50 322 Td
(  5. Security incidents must be reported within 1 hour of detection.) Tj
-50 -322 Td
50 310 Td
(  6. Annual penetration testing and quarterly vulnerability assessments required.) Tj
